  "title": "Sales Coordinator [Fashion / Clothing/ Experience in garment industry]",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Sales and Customer Service</li>\n  <li>Attend to walk-in customers, phone, and email inquiries</li>\n  <li>Liaise with suppliers and clients</li>\n  <li>Prepare quotations, tenders, purchase orders, delivery orders, data entry, etc.</li>\n  <li>Plan delivery schedules</li>\n  <li>General admin tasks, filing, inventory management, correspondence</li>\n</ul>\n<h5><strong>REQUIREMENTS:</strong></h5>\n<ul>\n  <li>Good interpersonal and communication skills</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently with minimal supervision</li>\n  <li>Experience in the garment/work wear industry is an added advantage</li>\n</ul>",
